TITLE

* Set the defaults for precision simulations
DEFAULTS                                                              PRECISIO
* Define the beam characteristics
BEAM
* Define the beam position
BEAMPOS
GEOBEGIN                                                              COMBNAME
    0    0          
* Black body
SPH blkbody    0.0 0.0 0.0 100000.0
* Void sphere
SPH void       0.0 0.0 0.0 10000.0
* Cylindrical target
RCC target     -0.054 0.023 0.998 500. 0.0 860. 100.
XZP xzp        -50.0
PLA pla        0.258819045 0.0 0.965925826 -0.18 2.7 98.
END
* Black hole
BLKBODY      5 +blkbody -void -xzp -pla
* Void around
VOID         5 +void -target -xzp -pla
* Target
TARGET       5 +target -xzp -pla
END
GEOEND
* ..+....1....+....2....+....3....+....4....+....5....+....6....+....7..
ASSIGNMA    BLCKHOLE   BLKBODY
ASSIGNMA      VACUUM      VOID
ASSIGNMA      COPPER    TARGET
* Set the random number seed
RANDOMIZ         1.0
* Set the number of primary histories to be simulated in the run
START
STOP
